How about a variation on Jerome's suggestion:

- The comment is before the element:
      (*> fun 1 *)
      val f : t
      (*> fun 2 *)
      val g : u
- The comment is after the element:
      val f : t
        (*< fun 1 *)
      val g : u
        (*< fun 2 *)

